import React from 'react'
import Input from './Input'

function FormikControl(props) {
    const {control, ...rest} = props
    
   switch(control) {
       case 'input': 
       return <Input {...rest} />
        case 'textarea':
        case 'select':
        case 'radio':
        case 'checkbox':
        case 'date':
        default: return null
   }
}

export default FormikControl
